    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - REMOVE - ROADRANGER VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="3">
        <title>ROADRANGER VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the two (2) mounting bolts from the Roadranger valve cover (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300707">Figure 7</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300707" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300707" filename="../figg13/G1300707.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 7. Remove Bolts From Roadranger Valve Cover</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Slide the Roadranger valve cover down (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300707">Figure 7</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Disconnect the air lines from the air fittings (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300708">Figure 8</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300708" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300708" filename="../figg13/G1300708.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 8. Disconnect Air Lines From Air Fittings</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen the jam nut at the Roadranger valve base (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1300709">Figure 9</hotlnk>). Rotate the Roadranger valve until the valve is removed.
            </para>
            <figure id="f1300709" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1300709" filename="../figg13/G1300709.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 9. Loosen Jam Nut at Roadranger Valve Base</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect the parts: nut, valve cover, air lines, sheathing, and O-rings from the lever shaft.
                Replace if necessary.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect the air fittings on the Roadranger valve; replace if necessary.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
